This is a program for tesing the quality of CRT/LCD screens. It displays
various patterns and allows you to estimate the quality of your CRT/LCD
monitor.

This is a postcardware (see the top of the file COPYING).

See the file INSTALL for instructions of how to build this program.

See the file NEW_TESTS for details on adding a new test screens.

The homepage of this program is

	http://screentest.sourceforge.net/

- Tobias Gruetzmacher (current maintainer)
- Jan "Yenya" Kasprzak (previous maintainer)
